name: TestTraceCE
cases: select * from t where a > 0 and a < 2
select * from t where a >= 1 and a < 10
select * from t where a < 3 or b < 4
select * from t where a = 1 and b = 2
select * from t where a < 5 or a > 10
select sum(t2.b) from t1 join t2 on t1.a = t2.b group by t2.a
select * from t1 left outer join (t3, t2) on t1.a = t2.b and t3.c = t2.a right outer join t4 on t4.b = t3.a
select * from t1 right outer join (select t2.a, t3.b from t2 join t3 on t2.b = t3.a) tt on t1.a = tt.b

select b, a in (select b from t2) from t1
select * from t1 where a not in (select b from t2)
select b, a not in (select b from t2) from t1
select * from t1 where exists (select b from t2 where t2.a = t1.c)
select * from t1 where not exists (select b from t2 where t2.a = t1.c)

select not exists (select b from t2 where t2.a = t1.c), c from t1
